videos.description: Texas Tech's Tommy Hamilton IV sinks a 3-pointer and gets fouled, creating a 4-point play.
videos.headline: Hamilton draws foul while hitting from deep

videos.description: Texas Tech's Jarrett Culver hits a corner 3 while Jaylen Fisher tries to distract him from the bench.
videos.headline: Culver knocks down 3 in front of the TCU bench

videos.description: Jarrett Culver pump fakes, drives down the baseline and finishes with a slam.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Culver takes it to the rack, throws it down

videos.description: Jarrett Culver scores 20 points off the bench in No. 10 Texas Tech's 83-71 victory over TCU.
videos.headline: Texas Tech takes down TCU for share of Big 12 lead
